  "comment": "LCB144: LCB144 LED Colour Bar\nThe LCB144 is a LED bar with 144 pieces SMD RGB LEDs. The LEDs are divided in 8 separately controllable sections. With each section having its own RGB colour setting in DMX mode. While using the fixture in stand-alone mode there are 3 pre-programmed shows that you can run automatically or sound activated, pick from the 16 pre-programmed automatic programs or create your own mixture of colours in RGB mode. The extra IEC output enables you to simply link the power of multiple units together into a single socket.",
